        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>μον <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἐρατὸν παῖδα <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>ῶν ἐθέμαν <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>μεν ἐνὶ τρισσαῖς δέκα <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>μει νανδαρεν<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">ἐν δ</supplied>όμασιν λοιπὰν δ' ἐλπίδ' ἐ<supplied reason="lost">μ</supplied>ῶν μελάθρων <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">δ</supplied>αίμων πικρὸς ἐμεῖο φέρων <supplied reason="lost">υἱ</supplied>ὸν εἶλε Κράτιππον <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>οὔνεκα τἀμὰ πάθη ξεῖν' ἐπι<supplied reason="lost">δ</supplied>ερκόμενος <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">θ</supplied>νατὸς ἐὼν μηδὲν λέξῃς <supplied reason="lost">μ</supplied>έγα τὰν γὰρ ἀλαθῆ <lb n="7"/>οὐθεὶς οἷδε τύχας οἷμον ὅ<supplied reason="lost">πᾳ</supplied> φέρεται
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bei dem kleineren der zwei Fragmente beträgt die Breite des Steins 20 cm, ansonsten sind die Maße gleich. Metrum: elegische Disticha. Reste von Füßen sind oben auf beiden Fragementen vorhanden. Nach den ersten drei gelesenen Buchstaben in Z. 1 folgen genau drei unsicher gelesene Buchstaben.</p>
            </div>
